{"tid":1882162,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"討論 其實連登既討論風氣實在太差","createTime":"2020-02-16T05:21:05.000Z","updateTime":"2020-02-17T02:35:53.000Z","uid":82829,"like":21,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"5b284aaacb75558e61e318bf963b01393587de71","tid":1882162,"uid":82829,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-16T05:21:05.000Z","msg":"有16歲男搶警槍！有醫護上前幫手阻止！！！！！<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1881507\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1881507</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n睇cm嚇親，有幾種論調實在我覺得唔得<br />\n一，oncc,報紙佬成日作新聞<br />\n藍絲：放場，毒果 黑記！！！<br />\n<br />\n二，太情緒主導<br />\n其實呢個講得太表面，更想講係連登仔唔岩心水就鬧人 黑__（今次係黑護）藍絲<br />\n見到有人駁，醫護撳住個靚仔都係本能，就會屌香港人係咪奴性到咁，你對唔對得住死咗既手足<br />\n<br />\n首先下下都搬手足上台，手足係咪愈嚟愈廉價啦？<br />\n其次見到對方意見不合就情緒勒索你。拒絕思考<br />\n<br />\n其實第二點可以話係造成呢度討論風氣愈嚟愈差既大原因之一，甚至唔少IG文宣太過煽情或多或少都係呢一點<br />\n<br />\n唔講太多，遲下再整理下"},{"pid":"530b9b39fea2babf9b296e6f25cdc1ed06696ef3","tid":1882162,"uid":115214,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-02-16T05:21:39.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"7328c1c7598016f0b496ac9ba6a24e074b7cf34b","tid":1882162,"uid":82829,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"530b9b39fea2babf9b296e6f25cdc1ed06696ef3","tid":1882162,"uid":115214,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-02-16T05:21:39.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-16T05:26:03.000Z","msg":"係<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />唔記得利串pr公司"},{"pid":"098c3a35a03930074897221648bdf728fff0a9f3","tid":1882162,"uid":115214,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-02-16T05:27:09.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"7ec0e7ad850408a903bd8cb483a7d0420e02990c","tid":1882162,"uid":82829,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"098c3a35a03930074897221648bdf728fff0a9f3","tid":1882162,"uid":115214,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"7328c1c7598016f0b496ac9ba6a24e074b7cf34b","tid":1882162,"uid":82829,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quo